    <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold">Build Principles</h4>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/70">
      <li>- Ship early, iterate often</li>
      <li>- Microservices from day one</li>
      <li>- Contract-first API design</li>
      <li>- Security by default</li>
      <li>- Observability built-in</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Technology Decisions</h3>
